LASER SAFETY NOTICE
================================================================================

This software controls laser projection hardware. Lasers can cause permanent
eye injury and skin burns, and their use is regulated in most jurisdictions.
This software is provided for educational and artistic purposes with no
warranty of any kind. You are solely responsible for operating your laser
safely and legally, including beam termination, audience-scanning rules, and
any permits your jurisdiction requires. The authors accept no liability for
injury or damage resulting from its use.
